description: TO ELECT A SPEAKER FOR THE 70TH HOUSE; NICHOLAS LONGWORTH (REP) VERSUS FINIS J. GARRETT (DEM.). VOTES FOR LONGWORTH ARE CODED 2, FOR GARRETT, 1.
